"# Heroism \n"
"_1st-level enchantment_    \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/heroism.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Casting Time:** 1 action    \n"
"**Range:** Touch    \n"
"**Components:** V, S    \n"
"**Duration:** Concentration, up to 1 minute \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/heroism.md:16
msgid ""
"A willing creature you touch is imbued with bravery. Until the spell ends, "
"the creature is immune to being frightened and gains temporary hit points "
"equal to your spellcasting ability modifier at the start of each of its "
"turns. When the spell ends, the target loses any remaining temporary hit "
"points from this spell."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/heroism.md:17
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**At Higher Levels.** When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd "
"level or higher, you can target one additional creature for each slot level "
"above 1st. \n"
msgstr ""
